Azhar seeks to reverse-sweep it away and only manages to run it off the face to the right of Mushfiq, who anticipates well. commentary: Rahat Ali to Mushfiqur Rahim, OUT The second grab does it for Alam. Good length slowy ball angling away outside off at 119.2ks, he slices it to Fawad at point, who messes it up on the first attempt. But recovers and pouches it on the second. Mushfiq raises his bat and acknowledges the applause as he walks back. He was undone by the change of pace
